data.description: Great weekender or possible VRBO property with this cute as a button lake cottage on the main channel of Lake Hamilton! Flat level yardoffers great views, a firepit to enjoy cool nights and a covered boat dock for summer fun! Home features fresh paint inside and out, newflooring, updated appliances and covered areas for vehicles and toys! New roof in 2021.
